<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>غ ض ن<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٣٥٧٩ - غ ض ن]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>غضَّنَ يغضِّن، تغضينًا، فهو مُغَضِّن، والمفعول مُغَضَّنٌ <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• غضَّنتِ السّماءُ:</span> دام مطرُها.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• غضَّن الشّيءَ:</span> ثنَّاه وجعَّده <span class="c1">"دخلْتُ عليه فغضَّن لي جبهتَه"</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>